HEADWORD: Spellful
<hw>Spell"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Abounding in spells,
or charms.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Here, while his eyes the learned leaves peruse,⟦br⟧
